@Version @Export

Package com.adobe.aemforms.fm.model

This package exports aem forms manager model classes.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AFFOptions
    AFFOptions represents the Adaptive Form Fragment Configurable properties that will be honored while creating Adaptive Form Fragment through FormGenerationService.
    AFOptions
    AFOptions represents the Adaptive Form Configurable properties that will be honored while creating Adaptive Form through FormGenerationService.
    FormGenerationResult
    This is returned after successful creation of asset by FormGenerationService
    FormOptions
    FormOptions represents the common configurable properties that will be honored while creating a Form through FormGenerationService.
    FormsetItem
    FormsetItem contains the information about a Form in the Form Set.
    FormsetOptions
    FormsetOptions represents the Form Set Configurable properties that will be honored while creating Form Set through FormGenerationService.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AFGenerator
    Enum used for specifying which software package was used to create an adaptive form using FormGenerationService.
    FormModel
    Enum used for specifying which Form model should be used while creating a form component using FormGenerationService.
    NameConflictAction
    An enumeration value that specifies an action to be implemented while creating form through FormGenerationService, in case a form with same name already exists in the repository, at the same location.
